---
import AppLayout from '../../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
const imagePath = '/acsm/loading-card.png?v=8';
---

<AppLayout title="ACSM Loading Card | GrassCutters">
  <div class="gc-page gc-acsm-card-page">
    <section class="gc-hero gc-hero--compact gc-acsm-card-hero">
      <div>
        <span class="gc-kicker">ACSM · Content Manager</span>
        <h1 class="gc-title">Imagen dinámica para el loading screen.</h1>
        <p class="gc-subtitle">
          Esta URL genera una tarjeta visual compacta con combo actual, top hotlaps reales y enlaces de comunidad para pegar en
          <strong>Loading Image URL</strong> dentro de ACSM.
        </p>
        <div class="gc-hero__meta">
          <span class="gc-chip gc-chip--accent">Wrapper activo</span>
          <span class="gc-chip">PNG dinámico</span>
          <span class="gc-chip">Formato estrecho</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="gc-live-panel gc-acsm-card-info">
        <div class="gc-live-panel__title"><span>URL para ACSM</span><strong>Lista</strong></div>
        <div class="gc-acsm-url-box" id="acsmUrlBox">https://grasscuttersracing.com{imagePath}</div>
        <div class="gc-acsm-actions">
          <button class="gc-btn gc-btn--primary" type="button" id="copyAcsmCardUrl">Copiar URL</button>
          <a class="gc-btn" href={imagePath} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Abrir imagen</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="gc-section gc-acsm-preview-section">
      <div class="gc-section-head">
        <div>
          <span class="gc-kicker">Preview</span>
          <h2>Vista previa actual</h2>
          <p>Ahora la tarjeta está pensada para entrar mejor en la columna estrecha del wrapper de Content Manager.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="gc-acsm-preview-frame">
        <img src={imagePath} alt="GrassCutters ACSM loading card" loading="eager" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="gc-acsm-steps-grid">
      <article class="gc-section gc-acsm-step-card">
        <span class="gc-kicker">Paso 1</span>
        <h2>Pégala en ACSM</h2>
        <p>Copia la URL y pégala aquí:</p>
        <code>Server → Content Manager Integration → Loading Image URL</code>
      </article>

      <article class="gc-section gc-acsm-step-card">
        <span class="gc-kicker">Paso 2</span>
        <h2>Wrapper activado</h2>
        <p>
          Mantén activo <strong>Content Manager Wrapper</strong>. El wrapper es lo que hace que ACSM cargue esta imagen externa.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="gc-section gc-acsm-step-card">
        <span class="gc-kicker">Paso 3</span>
        <h2>Refresco</h2>
        <p>
          La tarjeta se cachea 60 segundos. Si quieres forzar un refresco rápido, cambia la versión final de la URL, por ejemplo a
          <code>/acsm/loading-card.svg?v=8</code>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style is:global>
    .gc-acsm-card-page{
      display:grid;
      gap:clamp(18px,2.4vw,28px);
    }

    .gc-acsm-card-hero{
      padding-block:clamp(22px,3vw,34px)!important;
      margin:0;
    }

    .gc-acsm-card-hero .gc-title{
      font-size:clamp(2.9rem,6vw,5.8rem);
      line-height:.9;
      letter-spacing:-.075em;
      margin:8px 0 12px;
    }

    .gc-acsm-card-info,
    .gc-acsm-preview-section,
    .gc-acsm-step-card{
      margin:0;
      min-width:0;
    }

    .gc-acsm-url-box{
      margin-top:10px;
      padding:12px 14px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:14px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.035), rgba(255,255,255,.014));
      color:var(--text);
      font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;
      font-size:.92rem;
      line-height:1.45;
      overflow-wrap:anywhere;
    }

    .gc-acsm-actions{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:12px;
    }

    .gc-acsm-preview-frame{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:center;
      padding:18px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:24px;
      background:radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(157,255,63,.08), transparent 42%), linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.02), rgba(255,255,255,.01));
      box-shadow:0 22px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }

    .gc-acsm-preview-frame img{
      display:block;
      width:min(100%, 720px);
      max-width:720px;
      height:auto;
      border-radius:18px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:#020403;
    }

    .gc-acsm-steps-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));
      gap:clamp(16px,2vw,24px);
    }

    .gc-acsm-step-card h2{
      margin:.35rem 0 .7rem;
      color:var(--text);
      font-size:clamp(1.65rem,2.9vw,2.35rem);
      letter-spacing:-.05em;
      line-height:.98;
    }

    .gc-acsm-step-card p{
      color:var(--soft);
      line-height:1.55;
      margin:0 0 .85rem;
    }

    .gc-acsm-step-card code{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:.55rem .7rem;
      border-radius:12px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      color:var(--text);
      font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;
      overflow-wrap:anywhere;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px){
      .gc-acsm-steps-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    const btn = document.getElementById('copyAcsmCardUrl');
    const urlBox = document.getElementById('acsmUrlBox');
    const runtimeUrl = `${window.location.origin}/acsm/loading-card.png?v=8`;
    if (urlBox) urlBox.textContent = runtimeUrl;
    if (btn) {
      btn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
        try {
          await navigator.clipboard.writeText(runtimeUrl);
          btn.textContent = 'URL copiada';
          window.setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = 'Copiar URL'; }, 1400);
        } catch {
          window.prompt('Copia esta URL para ACSM', runtimeUrl);
        }
      });
    }
  </script>
</AppLayout>
